0万张，有“亚洲流行天王”之称，其音乐打破了亚洲原有单一的音乐主题形式，开创了多元化音乐创作和现代流行乐“中国风”的先河，为亚洲流行乐坛翻开了新的一页。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "1309": {"data": {"tag_id": 1309, "tag_name": "JAY", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "100475": {"data": {"tag_id": 100475, "tag_name": "田馥甄", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/1c0a9773d70e0e378f91c7f599bfb2e7867ba50f.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "田馥甄（Hebe），中国台湾女歌手、演员。台湾女子演唱团体S.H.E的成员之一。2000年参加“宇宙2000实力美少女争霸战”获得殿军，之后与参赛成员任家萱（Selina）、陈嘉桦（Ella）共同签入华研国际音乐，并组成S.H.E组合，2001年正式出道。[1]2010年以其本名发布首张个人专辑《To Hebe》，10月举办《Love!田馥甄To Hebe》巡回音乐会。2011年9月2日发布第二张专辑《My Love》，该专辑入围第23届金曲奖最佳国语专辑及最佳国语女歌手等提名，亦成为金曲奖入围最多项目的专辑之一。电视剧代表作有《真命天女》《斗牛，要不要》等。2013年将发行个人的第三张专辑《渺小》，于11月29日发行。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "50825": {"data": {"tag_id": 50825, "tag_name": "CP", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "719731": {"data": {"tag_id": 719731, "tag_name": "JH", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "1421242": {"dat